“What?! Breckenridge, am I the president?„

– James Buchanan, The Pig War

James Buchanan Jr. was an American politician and lawyer who served as the 15th President of the United States. He appeared in The Pig War.

Biography[]

Buchanan is seen as a timid, easily frightened US President, as depicted when he hides behind the window shades after the British arrive. He also tries to resolve issues using advice from his underlings, and hopes rather than orders people around.

Trivia[]

He was the last president before the american civil war. The more famous Abraham Lincoln became president after him.

Appearances[]

The Pig War
